---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - WattCostGuide" description="Privacy policy for WattCostGuide.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>WattCostGuide is designed to provide appliance electricity cost estimates with minimal personal data collection.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section article-block">
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      WattCostGuide does not require an account to use the calculators. Calculator values such as watts,
      hours, and electricity rate are processed in your browser and are not submitted through a form.
    </p>
    <p>
      Like most websites, hosting and analytics services may collect basic technical information such as
      browser type, pages visited, approximate location, referring pages, and device information.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section article-block">
    <h2>Cookies and advertising</h2>
    <p>
      WattCostGuide may use cookies or similar technologies for analytics, site performance, and advertising.
      If ads are displayed, third-party advertising partners may use cookies to personalize or measure ads
      according to their own policies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section article-block">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions or correction requests, use the contact page. This policy may be updated as the
      site adds analytics, advertising, or new features.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
